                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Teyvat :",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ]
                  ],
                  "ordered": true,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tutoriel",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Les koholasaures sont très doués pour nager à grande vitesse dans l'eau et ce sont également les seuls sauriens capables de nager dans le phlogistique liquide.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/ff2edb0ab3af7fff214848a71cf4d702_1474276264006109004.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Les koholasaures peuvent aussi manipuler librement la voie spirituelle.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/5246256061b9d8700340ad78b420cc67_6655285451402998222.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#80c0ff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Phlogistique liquide",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Du phlogistique qui ressemble à un liquide. Il contient une énergie thermique élevée, ce qui le rend dangereux.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/8b8829dbb4407f908e582ef8c9c08815_2059554647435258275.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Les koholasaures et certains du Peuple des sources maîtrisent une technique qui leur permet de traverser ces « eaux » pendant une courte période.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#80c0ff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Voies spirituelles",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Empruntez-les pour vous déplacer rapidement dans la direction du flux.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/1d7ccfc84730c18315d93778aba5bb26_5602435534758573186.gif"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Seuls les koholasaures ou les maîtres du Peuple des sources qui maîtrisent certaines techniques peuvent utiliser librement les voies spirituelles.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Veuillez noter que toutes les voies spirituelles ne sont pas complètes ou totalement sûres !",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#80c0ff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Vortex d'éjection",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tout ce qui tombe à l'intérieur sera projeté très haut.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/bccdcefee5f9e39cc6edf5ecb3f41532_5100788508188721605.gif"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Les koholasaures et les membres du Peuple des sources peuvent effectuer des sauts ultimes à haute altitude grâce aux vortex d'éjection !",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
